<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>File Metadata Microservice</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class='container'>
    <h1>File Metadata Microservice</h1>
    <h3>User stories:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>I can submit a FormData object that includes a file upload.</li>
      <li>When I submit something, I will receive the file size in bytes within the JSON response.</li>
    </ul>
    <h3>Please submit a file to view its filesize</h3>
    <form action="/upload" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="fileinput">File input</label>
        <input type="file" name="file" id="fileinput">
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="brn btn-primary">Submit</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</body>
</html>